snippet: The 21-year-old had been a member of the class of 2013 but was on leave and visiting friends, a university spokesman said.
abstract: New York City police say young woman, identified as Jessica Fingers, was found dead, possibly from drug overdose, in Columbia University dorm room.
lead_paragraph: The 21-year-old had been a member of the class of 2013 but was on leave and visiting friends, a university spokesman said.

headline.seo: Woman, 21, Is Found Dead in Columbia Dorm
headline.main: Woman Found Dead in Columbia Dorm
